des:
Your daily dose of positive vibes from Alexa.

Positive Vibes provides words of kindness whenever you need it.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Positive Vibes" or "Alexa, open Positive Vibes".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
